r />\n綠谷識放火？"},{"pid":"a0760cf8e7d16474daeeffcaa24ab68dd3c3a0c9","tid":292822,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T18:50:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我的英雄學園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主角係師父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n劇情都仲係初期 <br />\n點知佢後面會唔會彈個起強老豆出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識放火,其實我覺得佢老豆係NO2<br />\n因為個仔無個性,所以唔要佢,成件事好合理</blockquote><br />\n點睇都唔合理la<br />\n佢娶轟老母係想要佢個性<br />\n生個最強個性來超越allmight<br />\n點會搵綠谷老母呀<br />\n加上佢老母冇理由唔認得no.2<br />\n之後再講no.2係綠谷老豆成件事會好牽強<br />\n識噴火姐，個性會重複架麻<br />\n當然呢個只係我既睇法"},{"pid":"888a5473a8cfb900589a224bcb5d797892d70863","tid":292822,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T18:52:59.000Z","msg":"我的英雄學園"},{"pid":"56e303c7d666b38a9bea9f5006dc4dfe3a66a311","tid":292822,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T18:54:25.000Z","msg":"英雄學園"},{"pid":"b9c46a1e368f1faf1387b9571a7abf7f247af54e","tid":292822,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T19:05:39.000Z","msg":"旋風答家"},{"pid":"5811c7d6c771f22445ea5b030f9eed22d2be5267","tid":292822,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T19:05:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>旋風<span style=\"color: red;\">管</span>家</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8db4bf4d41a94345387959d285a1b26eff22b372","tid":292822,"uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T19:29:00.000Z","msg":"旋風管家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}